&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/NEW-YORK-PACHA-OFFER-LOGO1.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-8402&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/NEW-YORK-PACHA-OFFER-LOGO1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;NEW YORK- PACHA- OFFER- LOGO&quot; width=&quot;114&quot; height=&quot;60&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;Globally recognizable by the double-cherry logo, Pacha has been an icon on the nightlife scene for decades. Pacha New York, the only North American outpost, is a cavernous 30,000 square-foot space comprising four levels, each with a different look and vibe. The main dance floor in addition to various smaller VIP areas offer an ambiance for whatever your mood, whether high energy or lower profile and intimate. Casual but neat, fashionable and trendy attire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please contact Pacha via phone at +1-212-209-7510 or email at vip@pachanyc.com to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Nightlife Access to receive your special benefit.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to attend, number of guests, preferred time, cell phone or local (hotel) phone number and email address.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;For bottle/table service reservations, arrangements will be made at booking and payment will be required upon arrival. No deposit required at booking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;For last minute access to Pacha, please see a VIP host at the VIP door in front of the club. You will be required to show your Diners Club for access.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ages 18+ to enter; Age 21+ for bottle service and alcohol. ID must be provided.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;*Blackout dates may apply due to event buyouts. Special event/DJs may incur a charge.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Benefit is applicable for up to 4 guests in total.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dress code will be strictly enforced. Management reserves the right to refuse entry to guests due to visible intoxication, lack of proper ID, failure to adhere to dress code, or capacity limits.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Nightlife Access benefit.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Diners Club Card must be used for payment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Nightlife Access benefit may not be combined with other offers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating Nightclub/Lounge merchant.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reservations&nbsp;based on availability at the time of booking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nightclub/lounge participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Blackout dates may apply due to event buyouts. Special event/DJs may incur a charge.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

